summary: This is a brief email from December 11, 2021, attaching a defense witness list for an Epstein-related case. The sender asks the recipient to review the names in the list, noting that many have come up in the investigation, and suggests checking them through 'sentinel' (likely a database or system).

events.title: Defense Witness List Submission
events.description: A defense witness list is prepared and attached to an email for government review.

keyFacts: A defense witness list was submitted on or before December 10, 2021, in an Epstein-related case.
The email sender indicates that many names on the witness list have previously come up in the investigation.
The recipient is asked to review the names through 'sentinel', suggesting an investigative database or system is being used to vet witnesses.
